WEBVTT

00:02.506 --> 00:06.986
Make sure your script is open in Digital Micrograph.

00:07.658 --> 00:10.954
Click on your script, to make sure it is selected.

00:11.463 --> 00:16.807
Go to `File > Install Script...`.

00:17.286 --> 00:21.823
Click on the `Library` tab.

00:22.377 --> 00:26.564
You may rename your library in the `Name of library?` field

00:27.614 --> 00:34.418
Select either `Install for the current user only` or
`Install for all users`, depending on your needs.

00:34.899 --> 00:38.340
Click `Ok`.

00:38.931 --> 00:41.339
Your library is now installed.

00:41.886 --> 00:48.127
You may call its functions from other scripts
